#TellAFriendEmailText:
Hi,

I use iZettle and I think it is a great way to accept payments Sign up for an iZettle business account using my link and get your first transactions for free! 

iZettle lets anyone take secure card payments with their smartphone or tablet. The more you sell - the less you pay. Our Smart Rate starts at 2.75%% and drops to as little as 1.50%% per transaction. There are no fixed fees, no long-term contracts and it only takes 5 minutes to sign up.

Sign up for a business account using my link:

 %@

Best regards,
